1
00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:06,000
At 09:14 UTC, checkout latency crossed 900 milliseconds.

2
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:18,000
The first alert pointed to ap-south and incident commander opened INC-204.

3
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:42,000
错误码 E42 表示缓存写锁未释放，影响了三个工作节点。

4
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:56,000
The operator ran aurora cache inspect and identified worker-7 as the lock owner.

5
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:12,000
The lock was cleared under incident INC-204, and latency recovered by 09:22 UTC.

6
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:25,000
No nodes were restarted. Team Cygnus scheduled a follow-up for the ap-south region.
